<servlet>
		<servlet-name>dispatcher</servlet-name>
		<servlet-class>org.springframework.web.servlet.DispatcherServlet</servlet-class> --> this is known as front controller(DispatcherServlet) spring will giving it
		
		
		<init-param>
			<param-name>contextConfigLocation</param-name>
			<param-value>/WEB-INF/spring-mvc-demo-servlet.xml</param-value>
		</init-param>
		
		
		<load-on-startup>1</load-on-startup>  --> for initializing the DispatcherServlet if you not include this tag then DispatcherServlet will be initialized during the first request from client
	
</servlet>



